e. (Legislative Day January 7, 2026).", "date": "2026-01-08T05:00:00+00:00", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"upper\"}", "classification": ["introduction", "reading-1"], "related_entities": []}, {"description": "Motion to reconsider laid on the table Agreed to without objection.", "date": "2026-01-08T20:11:24+00:00", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": [], "related_entities": []}, {"description": "On passage Passed by the Yeas and Nays: 397 - 28 (Roll no. 7). (text: CR H151-199)", "date": "2026-01-08T20:11:23+00:00", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": [], "related_entities": []}, {"description": "Passed/agreed to in House: On passage Passed by the Yeas and Nays: 397 - 28 (Roll no. 7). (text: CR H151-199)", "date": "2026-01-08T20:11:23+00:00", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": ["passage"], "related_entities": []}, {"description": "On Retaining Divisions B and C Agreed to by the Yeas and Nays: 419 - 6 (Roll no. 6).", "date": "2026-01-08T20:04:09+00:00", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": [], "related_entities": []}, {"description": "Mr. Cole moved On Retaining Divisions B and C.", "date": "2026-01-08T19:58:06+00:00", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": [], "related_entities": []}, {"description": "On Retaining Division A Agreed to by the Yeas and Nays: 375 - 47 (Roll no. 5).", "date": "2026-01-08T19:58:00+00:00", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": [], "related_entities": []}, {"description": "Mr. Cole moved On Retaining Division A.", "date": "2026-01-08T19:31:48+00:00", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": [], "related_entities": []}, {"description": "Considered as unfinished business. (consideration: CR H209-211)", "date": "2026-01-08T19:31:02+00:00", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": [], "related_entities": []}, {"description": "POSTPONED PROCEEDINGS - The Chair put the question on retaining Division A of H.R. 6938 and pursuant to H. Res. 977 the yeas and nays were ordered. The Chair postponed further proceedings until a time to be announced.", "date": "2026-01-08T18:24:54+00:00", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": [], "related_entities": []}, {"description": "Pursuant to section 4(a) of H. Res. 977, the Chair will put the question on retaining Division A of the bill, and then retaining Divisions B and C.", "date": "2026-01-08T18:24:22+00:00", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": [], "related_entities": []}, {"description": "The previous question was ordered pursuant to the rule.", "date": "2026-01-08T18:24:17+00:00", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": [], "related_entities": []}, {"description": "DEBATE - The House proceeded with one hour of debate on H.R. 6938.", "date": "2026-01-08T17:29:46+00:00", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": [], "related_entities": []}, {"description": "Rule provides for consideration of H.R. 4593, H.R. 5184 and H.R. 6938. The resolution provides for consideration of H.R. 4593, H.R. 5184, and H.R. 6938 under a closed rule with one hour of general debate and provides for one motion to recommit on each bill.", "date": "2026-01-08T17:29:16+00:00", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": [], "related_entities": []}, {"description": "Considered under the provisions of rule H. Res. 977. (consideration: CR H151-205)", "date": "2026-01-08T17:29:11+00:00", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": [], "related_entities": []}, {"description": "UNANIMOUS CONSENT REQUEST - Mr. Cole asked unanimous consent that the question of retaining a portion of the bill on H.R. 6938 may be subject to postponement, as though under clause 8 of rule 20. Agreed to without objection.", "date": "2026-01-08T17:28:53+00:00", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": [], "related_entities": []}, {"description": "Rule H. Res. 977 passed House.", "date": "2026-01-07T22:33:14+00:00", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": [], "related_entities": []}, {"description": "Rules Committee Resolution H. Res. 977 Reported to House. Rule provides for consideration of H.R. 4593, H.R. 5184 and H.R. 6938. The resolution provides for consideration of H.R. 4593, H.R. 5184, and H.R. 6938 under a closed rule with one hour of general debate and provides for one motion to recommit on each bill.", "date": "2026-01-07T14:46:42+00:00", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": [], "related_entities": []}, {"description": "Referred to the Committee on Appropriations, and in addition to the Committee on the Budget, for a period to be subsequently determined by the Speaker, in each case for consideration of such provisions as fall within the jurisdiction of the committee concerned.", "date": "2026-01-06T05:00:00+00:00", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": ["referral-committee"], "related_entities": []}, {"description": "Introduced in House", "date": "2026-01-06T05:00:00+00:00", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": ["introduction"], "related_entities": []}], "sponsorships": [{"name": "Tom Cole", "classification": "primary", "entity_type": "person", "primary": true, "person_id": "~{\"name\": \"Tom Cole\"}", "organization_id": null}], "related_bills": [{"identifier": "S 2354", "legislative_session": "119", "relation_type": "companion"}, {"identifier": "HR 4754", "legislative_session": "119", "relation_type": "companion"}, {"identifier": "HR 5342", "legislative_session": "119", "relation_type": "companion"}, {"identifier": "HRES 977", "legis